| 10  | References        | [CrossRef](https://www.crossref.org/)                           |
| 11  | Telegram          | [Telegram](https://core.telegram.org/bots/api)                  |
| 12  | Weather           | [AirVisual](http://api.airvisual.com/)                          |
| 13  | Weather           | [OpenWeatherMap](https://openweathermap.org/api)                |
